  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the POV character, see <a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Tarly\" title=\"Samwell Tarly\">Samwell Tarly</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tarly\" title=\"House Tarly\"><img alt=\"House Tarly.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarly.svg/50px-House_Tarly.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarly.svg/75px-House_Tarly.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarly.svg/100px-House_Tarly.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lord</span><br />Samwell Tarly<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Savage Sam</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tarly\" title=\"House Tarly\"><img alt=\"House Tarly.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarly.svg/50px-House_Tarly.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarly.svg/75px-House_Tarly.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarly.svg/100px-House_Tarly.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Savage_Sam_Tarly_by_Wouter_Florusse_(The_Rise_of_the_Dragon).jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Savage Sam Tarly by Wouter Florusse (The Rise of the Dragon).jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2a/Savage_Sam_Tarly_by_Wouter_Florusse_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg/300px-Savage_Sam_Tarly_by_Wouter_Florusse_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"457\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2a/Savage_Sam_Tarly_by_Wouter_Florusse_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg/450px-Savage_Sam_Tarly_by_Wouter_Florusse_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2a/Savage_Sam_Tarly_by_Wouter_Florusse_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg/600px-Savage_Sam_Tarly_by_Wouter_Florusse_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Savage Sam Tarly by Wouter Florusse for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nSavage Sam<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Horn_Hill\" title=\"Lord of Horn Hill\">Lord of Horn Hill</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Tarly\" title=\"House Tarly\">House Tarly</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornish_Marches\" title=\"Dornish Marches\">Marcher</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aenys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aenys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sons_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Sons of the Dragon\">The Sons of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Samwell Tarly</b>, known as <b>Savage Sam</b>, was the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Horn_Hill\" title=\"Horn Hill\">Horn Hill</a> and head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tarly\" title=\"House Tarly\">House Tarly</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aenys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aenys I Targaryen\">Aenys I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aenys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aenys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Samwell_Tarly_(lord)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>When the <a href=\"/index.php/Vulture_King_(Aenys_I)\" title=\"Vulture King (Aenys I)\">Vulture King</a> began raiding the <a href=\"/index.php/Dornish_Marches\" title=\"Dornish Marches\">Dornish Marches</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/37_AC\" title=\"37 AC\">37&#160;AC</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Orys_Baratheon\" title=\"Orys Baratheon\">Orys Baratheon</a> was joined by <a href=\"/index.php/Marcher_lords\" title=\"Marcher lords\">marcher lords</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Dornish_War\" title=\"Second Dornish War\">Second Dornish War</a>. The Vulture King soon abandoned his siege of <a href=\"/index.php/Nightsong\" title=\"Nightsong\">Nightsong</a>, but Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Harmon_Dondarrion\" title=\"Harmon Dondarrion\">Harmon Dondarrion</a> and Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Ellyn_Caron\" title=\"Ellyn Caron\">Ellyn Caron</a> cut off his retreat, while Samwell suddenly appeared in the <a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornish</a> line of march with several thousand <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a> and archers.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In what became known as the <a href=\"/index.php/Vulture_Hunt\" title=\"Vulture Hunt\">Vulture Hunt</a>, it is claimed that Savage Sam's <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_steel\" title=\"Valyrian steel\">Valyrian steel</a> sword, <a href=\"/index.php/Heartsbane\" title=\"Heartsbane\">Heartsbane</a>, was crimson from hilt to point with the blood of the dozens of Dornish outlaws he had slain.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aenys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aenys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> The Dornish host was defeated and the Vulture King was taken alive and tied naked between two posts by Sam. The Vulture King soon perished of thirst and exposure.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Samwell was among those granted gold, honors, and offices by a grateful King <a href=\"/index.php/Aenys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aenys I Targaryen\">Aenys I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The Lord of Horn Hill was present at the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Wedding\" title=\"Golden Wedding\">Golden Wedding</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/49_AC\" title=\"49 AC\">49&#160;AC</a>, but it is unknown if this was Samwell.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Samwell_Tarly_(lord)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7